Package tr.edu.ku.devnull.needforspear.Model.UIModels

Class NoblePhantasm

java.lang.Object
tr.edu.ku.devnull.needforspear.Model.UIModels.NoblePhantasm
public class NoblePhantasm
extends java.lang.Object
NoblePhantasm is a class which contains all the size, movement and map specifications for the noble phantasm to operate within the game, as well as initializing the noble phantasm itself.
